    "Name": "Dengier DG1-OF",
    "Details": "The DG1-OF configuration replaces conventional direct fire weapons with twin Plasma Rifles, using superheated plasma to both damage and overheat targets. ER Flamers and Heavy Machine Guns round out an anti-infantry and heat-denial suite that makes this variant particularly brutal against lightly armored or heat-sensitive opposition. Seventeen double heat sinks manage the considerable self-generated heat from sustained plasma fire.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Protected Actuators</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.05</color></b>",
